5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVanityFair%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40VanityFair%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20know%20when%20your%20veterinary%20experts%20call%20a%20goat%20a%20dog%2C%20and%20your%20forensic%20experts%20say%20a%20photo%20taken%20in%20Patagonia%20was%20taken%20in%20Korea%2C%20that%20you%E2%80%99ve%20joined%20the%20ranks%20of%20supermarket%20tabloids.%20Keep%20telling%20America%20that%20up%20is%20down%20if%20you%20want.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20keep%20talking%20about%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSGX3QpoaRZ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSGX3QpoaRZ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr%20(%40RobertKennedyJr)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRobertKennedyJr%2Fstatus%2F1808220327194825142%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Vanity%20Fair%20article%20also%20contained%20allegations%20from%20%3Cspan%3EEliza%20Cooney%2C%20who%20said%20she%20worked%20for%20Kennedy%20as%20a%20babysitter%20in%201998%2C%20when%20she%20was%2023.%20On%20one%20occasion%2C%20Kennedy%20groped%20her%20in%20the%20kitchen%20of%20his%20family%20home%20and%20touched%20her%20hips%20and%20breasts%2C%20Cooney%20told%20Vanity%20Fair.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20those%20accusations%20on%20the%20podcast%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20church%20boy%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%2C%20very%20rambunctious%20youth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20added%20that%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bmany%20skeletons%20in%20my%20closet%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthat%20if%20they%20could%20all%20vote%2C%20I%20could%20run%20for%20king%20of%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20would%20not%20comment%20on%20details%20from%20%26quot%3B30-year-old%26quot%3B%20stories%20that%20Vanity%20Fair%20was%20recycling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%