vers%20will%20get%20some%20sort%20of%20sick%20pay%20and%20a%20healthcare%20stipend%20as%20unpaid%20time%20off%20caused%20by%20illness%20and%20healthcare%20insurance%20borne%20entirely%20by%20drivers%20are%20both%20extremely%20expensive%20for%20self-employed%20drivers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b768492-c291-41f4-b4b5-8212067b9f7c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20minimum%20wage%20legislation%20is%20working%20in%20other%20states%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20handful%20of%20states%20have%20already%20agreed%20with%20Uber%2C%20Lyft%2C%20and%20other%20ride-hailing%20and%20delivery%20companies%20on%20citywide%20or%20statewide%20plans.%20Lobbying%20efforts%20by%20drivers%20are%20underway%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.cityofchicago.org%2FEthics%2FLobbying-data-Uber%2F9p52-uwar%2Fabout_data%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChicago%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kptv.com%2F2024%2F02%2F14%2Fuber-lyft-drivers-portland-hold-rally-ask-fair-wages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPortland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.12onyourside.com%2F2024%2F02%2F14%2Fseveral-rideshare-delivery-drivers-go-strike-richmond%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVirginia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Avedian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20California%20passed%20Proposition%2022%2C%20which%20kept%20drivers%20as%20independent%20contractors%20but%20gave%20them%20benefits%20such%20as%20guaranteed%20pay.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uber.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fuber-invests-more-than-1-billion-in-prop-22-benefits-for-ca-drivers-and-couriers%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMinimum%2520Earnings%2520Guarantee%253A%2520Earners%2520are%2Caccept%2520a%2520ride%2520or%2520delivery.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20receive%20at%20least%20120%25%20of%20minimum%20wage%2C%20which%20is%20now%20%2416%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20%240.35%20a%20mile%20while%20completing%20a%20ride%20or%20delivery.%20Qualifying%20drivers%20can%20get%20up%20to%20%24489.54%20a%20month%20for%20healthcare%20insurance%20costs%2C%20and%20drivers%20get%20additional%20insurance%20covering%20medical%20expenses%20and%20lost%20income%20resulting%20from%20job-related%20illness%20or%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20California%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20challenging%20the%20legality%20of%20Proposition%2022%20over%20concerns%20about%20classifying%20drivers%20as%20independent%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20from%20the%20UC%20Berkeley%20Labor%20Center%20and%20the%20Center%20for%20Wage%20and%20Employment%20Dynamics%20suggests%20even%20with%20these%20guarantees%20in%20place%2C%20drivers%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20San%20Francisco%20had%20net%20hourly%20earnings%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-doordash-drivers-earn-below-minimum-wage-tips-study-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewell%20below%20minimum%20wage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20with%20tips%20%E2%80%94%20net%20hourly%20pay%20with%20tips%20for%20passenger%20drivers%20in%20California%20is%20%249.09%2C%20while%20for%20delivery%20drivers%20it's%20%2413.62.%20Similar%20results%20were%20found%20in%20the%20Boston%2C%20Chicago%2C%20and%20Seattle%20metros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20early%20June%2C%20the%20minimum%20hourly%20rate%20for%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20drivers%20in%20New%20York%20outside%20of%20New%20York%20City%20was%20raised%20to%20%2426.78.%20Drivers%20in%20New%20York%20City%20receive%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nyc.gov%2Fsite%2Ftlc%2Fabout%2Fdriver-pay-rates.page%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20decided%20on%20by%20the%20Taxi%20and%20Limousine%20Commission.%20Drivers%20also%20received%20new%20benefits%20like%20sick%20leave%2C%20training%2C%20and%20chat%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20after%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20paid%20New%20York%20%24328%20million%20over%20wage%20theft%20claims%2C%20though%20both%20companies%20denied%20wrongdoing.%20The%20companies%20have%20been%20under%20fire%20recently%20after%20Uber%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-06-24%2Fuber-is-locking-out-new-york-city-drivers-mid-shift-to-lower-minimum-pay%3Fsrnd%3Dundefined%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20locked%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20New%20York%20City%20drivers%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20their%20shifts%20in%20opposition%20to%20a%20minimum%20wage%20rule%2C%20a%20decision%20Lyft%20said%20it's%20considering%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20struck%20a%20deal%20to%20pay%20Minnesota%20drivers%20%241.28%20per%20mile%20and%20%240.31%20per%20minute%20minimum.%20The%20two%20companies%20threatened%20to%20pull%20out%20of%20Minneapolis%2C%20which%20has%20a%20minimum%20wage%20for%20large%20businesses%20of%20%2415.57.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20gig%20driver%20who%20is%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%3F%20Are%20you%20driving%20into%20your%20retirement%20years%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmassachusetts-uber-lyft-driving-minimum-wage-gig-work-lobbying-competition-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720000443000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66843fed1f0c1cd6d730dd8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmassachusetts-uber-lyft-driving-minimum-wage-gig-work-lobbying-competition-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uber%20and%20Lyft%20settle%20to%20pay%20Massachusetts%20drivers%20%2432.50%20per%20hour%20for%20time%20spent%20completing%20a%20ride%2C%20as%20well%20as%20paid%20sick%20leave%20and%20accident%20insurance.%