just%2060%20MPs.%20The%20verbal%20sparring%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20turned%20acrimonious%20and%20personal%2C%20reflecting%20the%20recently%20concluded%20election%20campaign%20dynamics%20and%20entrenched%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoth%20Congress%20And%20BJP%20Remain%20Steadfast%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20aims%20to%20sustain%20momentum%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20remains%20resolute%20not%20to%20concede%20further%20ground.%20The%20shift%20in%20strength%2C%20allocation%20of%20time%20for%20parties%2C%20and%20the%20calibre%20of%20speakers%20on%20both%20sides%20will%20significantly%20influence%20proceedings%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20During%20the%20recent%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20debate%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20as%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20spoke%20for%20nearly%20an%20hour%20and%2040%20minutes%20out%20of%20the%20allotted%2016%20hours%20-%20roughly%2015%25%20of%20the%20total%20time%20allotted%20to%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETime%20allocations%20are%20based%20on%20Lok%20Sabha%20strength.%20During%20the%20No%20Confidence%20Motion%20of%20August%202023%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%20around%2045%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20while%20the%20Congress'%20share%20was%20just%2018%25%20With%20the%20BJP's%20friendly%20parties%20(the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%2C%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party)%20losing%20ground%20in%20recent%20elections%2C%20their%20allocation%20has%20shifted%20notably%20to%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-in-parliament-dig-at-rahul-gandhi-hug-wink-in-parliament-6019167%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0'Hug%2C%20Wink%20In%20Parliament'%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20Dig%20At%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20prominent%20speakers%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches%2C%20such%20as%20Smriti%20Irani%2C%20were%20notably%20absent.%20Conversely%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20parties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20has%20bolstered%20the%20opposition%2C%20particularly%20with%20effective%20speakers%20in%20fluent%20Hindi.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20speech%2C%20noted%20for%20its%20sarcasm%20without%20overt%20anger%2C%20followed%20Rahul's%20assertive%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERahul's%20Performance%20As%20LoP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Monday's%20session%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20launched%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20highlighting%20issues%20including%20inflation%2C%20unemployment%2C%20NEET%2C%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20for%20crops%2C%20the%20Agniveer%20scheme%2C%20and%20Hindutva%2C%20aiming%20to%20put%20the%20government%20on%20the%20defensive.%20Top%20ministers%2C%20including%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20intervened%20during%20Rahul's%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rahul%20addressed%20critical%20issues%2C%20some%20noted%20the%20absence%20of%20specific%20data%20and%20figures%20in%20his%20speech.%20There%20is%20already%20an%20ongoing%20debate%20over%20Rahul's%20performance%20in%20his%20role%20as%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20with%20supporters%20arguing%20his%20assertiveness%20marks%20a%20significant%20political%20presence%20that%20cannot%20be%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20new%20to%20controversy%2C%20Rahul%20made%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20stating%2C%20that%20those%20who%20called%20themselves%20Hindu%20only%20talked%20about%20violence%2C%20hatred%2C%20and%20untruth.%20PM%20Modi%20rebutted%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-parliament-speech-expunged-pm-modi-bjp-om-birla-every-mps-right-rahul-gandhi-questions-expunging-of-parts-of-speech-6016341%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%26quot%3BEvery%20MP's%20Right%26quot%3B%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Questions%20Expunging%20Of%20Parts%20Of%20Speech%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferences%20in%20Rahul's%20speech%20to%20to%20Hinduism%20and%20violence%2C%20two%20prominent%20industrialists%2C%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%2C%20and%20NEET%2C%20were%20expunged.%20The%20LoP%20subsequently%20wrote%20to%20the%20Speaker%20questioning%20the%20decision%20and%20demanding%20the%20restoration%20of%20his%20remarks%20in%20parliamentary%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi's%20Address%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20delivered%20the%20concluding%20remarks%20on%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20His%20speech%2C%20lasting%20around%202.5%20hours%2C%20was%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20and%20Rahul.%20Throughout%20his%20address%2C%20the%20opposition%20shouted%20slogans%2C%20prompting%20Modi%20to%20use%20headphones%20to%20counter%20the%20noise.%20Despite%20the%20interruptions%2C%20Modi's%20speech%2C%20though%20not%20entirely%20audible%2C%20gave%20enough%20hints%20of%20the%20things%20to%20come%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20criticised%20the%20opposition's%20maturity%20level%2C%20noting%20that%20while%20the%20treasury%20benches%20listened%20to%20Rahul's%20speech%20with%20interjections%20rather%20than%20shouting%20slogans%2C%20the%20opposition%20did%20not%20afford%20the%20same%20respect%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20Expressing%20displeasure%20at%20the%20sloganeering%2C%20Modi%20referred%20to%20Rahul%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fthose-saying-balak-buddhi-akhilesh-yadav-on-pm-s-jab-at-rahul-gandhi-810298%5C%22%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ebalak%20buddhi%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20(childish)%20and%20mocked%20how%20a%20party%20celebrating%2099%20out%20of%20543%20seats%20was%20acting%20as%20if%20it%20had%20won%2099%20out%20of%20100.%20He%20criticised%20the%20Congress%20party's%20promise%20of%20transferring%20Rs.%201%20lakh%20to%20women's%20bank%20accounts%2C%20highlighting%20the%20public's%20scepticism%20about%20similar%20promises%20made%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20accused%20Rahul%20of%20resorting%20to%20drama%20to%20garner%20sympathy%2C%20pointing%20out%20his%20bail%20status%20in%20alleged%20financial%20misconduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20debate%20was%20disappointing%20for%20both%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20ruling%20party.%20BJP%20leaders%20neglected%20discussion%20around%20their%20agenda%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20while%20the%20opposition%20failed%20to%20engage%20in%20constructive%20criticism%20and%20effectively%20address%20issues%20like%20NEET.%20Both%20sides%20instead%20resorted%20to%20mudslinging%2C%20seemingly%20forgetting%20that%20the%20elections%20were%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20session's%20outcome%20suggests%20the%20potential%20for%20more%20disruptions%20and%20chaos%20in%20Parliament.%20Both%20sides%20must%20reconcile%20with%20the%20electoral%20mandate%20and%20strive%20for%20a%20fresh%20start%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Budget%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720000260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fvi7988n_parliament-debate_625x300_03_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fparliament-debate-is-just-a-teaser-for-more-disruption-and-chaos-6024255%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Overall%2C%20the%20debate%20was%20disappointing%20for%20both%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%20Both%20sides%20resorted%20to%20mudslinging%2C%20seemingly%20forgetting%20that%20the%20elections%20wer