.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJD%20MPs%20this%20time%20will%20not%20be%20confined%20to%20speaking%20on%20issues%20only%2C%20but%20are%20determined%20to%20agitate%20if%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20ignores%20Odisha's%20interests.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20Mr%20Patnaik%20has%20given%20clear%20instructions%20to%20BJD%20MPs%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20state's%20people%20in%20the%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20more%20support%20to%20BJP%2C%20only%20opposition.%20We%20may%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20Odisha.%20The%20BJD%20president%20asked%20us%20to%20act%20as%20a%20strong%20and%20vibrant%20opposition%20if%20the%20NDA%20government%20continues%20to%20ignore%20the%20genuine%20demands%20of%20Odisha%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patra%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719999960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fjvbatgd_naveen-patnaik-narendra-modi_625x300_03_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-naveen-patnaik-bjd-once-bjps-friend-in-need-joins-opposition-walkout-after-odisha-rout-6024838%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Naveen%20Patnaik-led%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%2C%20once%20the%20BJP's%20friend%20in%20need%20whose%20support%20helped%20several%20contentious%20Bills%20clear%20Rajya%20Sabha%20during%20Modi%202.0%2C%20were%20on%20the%20other%20side%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-naveen-patnaik-bjd-once-bjps-friend-in-need-joins-opposition-walkout-after-odisha-rout-6024838%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-naveen-patnaik-bjd-once-bjps-friend-in-need-joins-opposition-walkout-after-odisha-rout-6024838%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-naveen-patnai