mp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Flatentview-analytics-bags-70-stake-in-decision-point-for-39-1-million-124070300534_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM's%20%26quot%3BRemote%26quot%3B%20Swipe%20At%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Opposition%20Walks%20Out%20Of%20Rajya%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20cannot%20listen%20to%20replies%20of%20questions%20they%20raised%20and%20can%20only%20run%20away%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20today%20as%20the%20Opposition%20walked%20out%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20during%20his%20reply%20to%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20to%20the%20President's%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20MPs%20led%20by%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20walked%20out%20after%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20refused%20to%20grant%20him%20permission%20to%20intervene%20during%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition's%20walkout%20followed%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20swipe%20at%20former%20Congress%20chief%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%20%26quot%3BThese%20people%20are%20used%20to%20running%20the%20government%20on%20auto%20pilot%20and%20remote%20pilot.%20They%20don't%20believe%20in%20working%2C%20they%20just%20know%20how%20to%20wait%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remark%20was%20aimed%20at%20Mrs%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20has%20often%20been%20accused%20by%20the%20BJP%20of%20running%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20from%20behind%20the%20scenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20hard%20work.%20We%20would%20step%20up%20what%20we%20did%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20Considering%20what%20our%20dreams%20are%2C%20these%2010%20years%20were%20an%20appetiser.%20The%20main%20course%20has%20started%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Opposition%20were%20heard%20demanding%20that%20Mr%20Kharge%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20be%20allowed%20to%20intervene.%20Opposition%20MPs%20raised%20slogans%20of%20%26quot%3BLOP%20ko%20bolne%20do%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Kharge%2C%20too%2C%20was%20heard%20requesting%20the%20Chairman%20repeatedly%20for%20an%20opportunity%20to%20intervene.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20put%20forth%20our%20views%2C%20please%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2081-year-old%20said.%20The%20slogans%20then%20changed%20to%20%26quot%3Bjhoot%20bolna%20band%20karo%20(stop%20lying)%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsharm%20karo%20(please%20have%20shame)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said%20that%20the%20Opposition's%20conduct%20is%20not%20appropriate.%20%26quot%3BI%20strongly%20condemn%20unparliamentary%20practice%2C%20please%20take%20your%20seats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20slogans%20continued%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20paused%20his%20speech%20on%20the%20government's%20achievements%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMr%20Chairman%2C%20the%20country%20is%20watching.%20Those%20spreading%20lies%20do%20not%20have%20the%20guts%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20truth.%20They%20cannot%20sit%20and%20listen%20to%20the%20answers%20to%20the%20questions%20they%20raised.%20They%20are%20insulting%20the%20Upper%20House%2C%20its%20traditions.%20The%20people%20have%20defeated%20them%20in%20every%20way%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20any%20other%20option%20other%20than%20shouting%20in%20alleys.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSloganeering%2C%20shouting%20and%20running%20away%2C%20this%20is%20their%20destiny%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChairman%20Dhankhar%20then%20said%20the%20Opposition's%20conduct%20was%20%26quot%3Bagonising%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20gave%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20the%20opportunity%20to%20speak%20without%20disruptions.%20They%20did%20not%20leave%20the%20House%2C%20they%20left%20decorum.%20They%20did%20not%20turn%20their%20backs%20to%20me%2C%20but%20to%20the%20Constitution.%20They%20did%20not%20disrespect%20us%2C%20they%20disrespected%20the%20oath%20they%20have%20taken.%20There%20cannot%20be%20a%20bigger%20disrespect%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20I%20condemn%20their%20conduct.%26quot%3B%20The%20Chairman%20said%20he%20hopes%20the%20Opposition%20MPs%20will%20%26quot%3Bintrospect%26quot%3B%20and%20return%20back%20to%20the%20path%20of%20duty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20today%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20offensive%20of%20targeting%20the%20Congress%20over%20Emergency%20to%20counter%20the%20Opposition's%20Constitution%20push.%20%26quot%3BI%20say%20with%20all%20seriousness%20that%20Congress%20is%20the%20biggest%20opponent%20of%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%201977%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20held%20after%20the%20Emergency%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20people%20of%20the%20country%20had%20then%20voted%20to%20restore%20democracy.%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20no%20bigger%20election%20to%20protect%20the%20Constitution.%20In%201977%2C%20the%20country%20showed%20democracy%20runs%20in%20its%20veins%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20the%20election%20this%20year%20was%20to%20defend%20the%20Constitution%2C%20then%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20found%20us%20up%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719999060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fkmmmuh58_pm-modi_625x300_03_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-earlier-work-was-appetiser-main-course-begins-now-pm-modi-in-rajya-sabha-6023605%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20last%2010%20years%20of%20BJP%20rule%20at%20the%20Centre%20was%20%26quot%3Bappetiser%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bmain%20course%26quot%3B%20has%20started%20only%20now%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20told%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today%20as%20he%20laid%20down%20his%20government's%20plans%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years.%22%2C%22author