2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fhow-trash-carrying-balloons-from-north-korea-have-led-to-major-flight-disruptions-in-south-korea%2Famp_articleshow%2F111450724.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fhow-trash-carrying-balloons-from-north-korea-have-led-to-major-flight-disruptions-in-south-korea%2Famp_articleshow%2F111450724.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Is%20India%20Ready%20To%20Go%20All-EV%20By%202034%3F%20Absolutely%20Not%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ftol1er78_ev_625x300_03_July_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20Transport%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20made%20a%20startling%20announcement%3A%20the%20Union%20Government%20plans%20to%20eliminate%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20vehicles%20by%202034%2C%20replacing%20them%20primarily%20with%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs).%20This%20bold%20move%2C%20touted%20as%20a%20step%20toward%20reducing%20carbon%20emissions%20and%20achieving%20climate%20goals%2C%20could%20lead%20India%20into%20a%20crisis%20of%20epic%20proportions%20if%20not%20meticulously%20planned%20and%20executed.%20The%20hidden%20carbon%20footprint%20of%20EVs%2C%20the%20inadequacy%20of%20our%20renewable%20energy%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20strain%20on%20our%20power%20grid%20and%20the%20economic%20and%20geopolitical%20ramifications%2C%20all%20paint%20a%20grim%20picture%20of%20a%20policy%20that%20could%20backfire%20disastrously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.5%20Times%20Petrol%20Or%20Diesel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electricity%20required%20to%20charge%20EVs%20often%20comes%20from%20coal-based%20power%20plants%2C%20which%20are%20major%20carbon%20emitters.%20As%20per%20an%20analysis%2C%20which%20used%20the%20Tata%20Nexon%20as%20a%20benchmark%20(assuming%20an%2080%25%20charging%20efficiency%2C%20our%20current%20energy%20mix%2C%2033%25%20efficiency%20of%20a%20coal%20power%20plant%2C%20and%20approximately%2015%25%20transmission%20loss%20on%20the%20grid)%2C%20charging%20the%2040.5%20kWh%20battery%20of%20the%20Nexon%20EV%20Max%20would%20require%20approximately%2026.7%20kg%20of%20coal.%20This%20is%202.5%20times%20the%20petrol%20or%20diesel%20needed%20for%20the%20same%20distance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20Not%20So%20Bad%20After%20All%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20true%20that%20EVs%20generally%20have%20higher%20emissions%20during%20the%20production%20phase%20compared%20to%20internal%20combustion%20engine%20vehicles%20(ICEVs).%20This%20is%20due%20to%20the%20energy-intensive%20process%20of%20battery%20manufacturing.%20For%20instance%2C%20producing%20a%20medium-sized%20EV%20typically%20results%20in%20about%2015-68%25%20more%20emissions%20than%20producing%20a%20comparable%20gasoline%20car.%20However%2C%20over%20their%20lifetime%2C%20EVs%20produce%20significantly%20fewer%20emissions%20than%20ICEVs%2C%20primarily%20due%20to%20the%20elimination%20of%20tailpipe%20emissions.%20In%20countries%20with%20a%20high%20share%20of%20renewable%20energy%2C%20EVs%20can%20reduce%20emissions%20by%20up%20to%2070-90%25%20compared%20to%20ICEVs.%20In%20areas%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20coal%2C%20EVs%20still%20typically%20result%20in%20lower%20overall%20emissions%20compared%20to%20gasoline%20or%20diesel%20vehicles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20accounting%20for%20the%20entire%20supply%20chain%2C%20including%20electricity%20generation%20(well-to-wheel%20analysis)%2C%20the%20reduction%20in%20emissions%20varies%20but%20can%20range%20from%2030-60%25%20depending%20on%20the%20region's%20energy%20sources.%20According%20to%20the%20International%20Council%20on%20Clean%20Transportation%20(ICCT)%2C%20an%20average%20EV%20in%20Europe%20is%20responsible%20for%2066-69%25%20less%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20over%20its%20lifetime%20compared%20to%20an%20average%20gasoline%20car%2C%20considering%20the%20current%20energy%20mix.%20In%20the%20U.S.%2C%20an%20EV%20charged%20using%20the%20national%20average%20electricity%20mix%20emits%20about%20half%20as%20much%20CO2%20per%20mile%20as%20a%20typical%20new%20gasoline%20car.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20the%20share%20of%20renewable%20energy%20increases%20in%20electricity%20grids%20worldwide%2C%20the%20emissions%20associated%20with%20EVs%20will%20continue%20to%20decrease%2C%20to%20nearly%20zero%20if%20the%20grid%20were%20100%25%20renewable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20has%20made%20significant%20progress%20in%20renewable%20energy%2C%20with%20solar%20and%20wind%20contributing%2019%25%20and%2010%25%20respectively%20to%20the%20total%20installed%20capacity%2C%20their%20intermittent%20nature%20means%20they%20cannot%20reliably%20meet%20the%20demand%20for%20EV%20charging%2C%20which%20often%20occurs%20overnight.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20will%20likely%20need%20to%20rely%20more%20on%20coal-based%20power%2C%20which%20currently%20generates%20about%2076%25%20of%20our%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransitioning%20to%20an%20all-EV%20future%20by%202034%20will%20require%20doubling%20our%20power%20generation%20capacity.%20However%2C%20the%20government's%20current%20plan%20is%20to%20add%20517%20GW%20by%202032%2C%20which%20seems%20unlikely.%20Over%20the%20past%20nine%20years%2C%20we've%20only%20added%20139.62%20GW.%20Additionally%2C%20our%20power%20grid%2C%20which%20already%20struggles%20to%20meet%20current%20demands%2C%20will%20need%20extensive%20upgrades.%20This%20includes%20doubling%20the%20number%20of%20transformers%2C%20feeders%2C%20and%20transmission%20lines%20to%20prevent%20frequent%20power%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20and%20Geopolitical%20Implications%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20transition%20to%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%20is%20not%20just%20about%20reducing%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20it%20also%20involves%20complex%20economic%20and%20geopolitical%20factors.%20While%20decreasing%20reliance%20on%20crude%20oil%20imports%20is%20a%20valid%20goal%2C%20India%20also%20imports%20significant%20amounts%20of%20coal%2C%20and%20shifting%20to%20EVs%20will%20merely%20shift%20dependency%20from%20oil%20to%20coal%20and%20critical%20minerals%20like%20lithium%2C%20cobalt%2C%20and%20nickel.%20These%20minerals%20are%20mainly%20sourced%20from%20countries%20like%20China%2C%20which%20introduces%20new%20strategic%20risks%20given%20India's%20strained%20relations%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20EV%20supply%20chain%20is%20susceptible%20to%20geopolitical%20instability%20and%20trade%20disputes.%20To%20mitigate%20these%20risks%2C%20India%20is%20forming%20international%20alliances%20and%20partnerships%20with%20countries%20like%20Japan%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20and%20Australia.%20These%20collaborations%20aim%20to%20diversify%20supply%20sources%2C%20promote%20technological%20exchange%2C%20and%20enhance%20energy%20security.%20Economically%2C%20reducing%20oil%20imports%20might%20improve%20India's%20current%20account%20deficits%2C%20but%20increased%20imports%20of%20critical%20minerals%20and%20high-tech%20components%20could%20offset%20these%20gains.%20The%20domestic%20EV%20industry%20also%20faces%20challenges%20in%20competing%20with%20established%20global%20players%2C%20potentially%20leading%20to%20job%20losses%20and%20economic%20instability.%20Therefore%2C%20strategic%20policies%20are%20needed%20to%20support%20local%20industries%20and%20ensure%20sustainable%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20India's%20move%20to%20EVs%20will%20impact%20global%20energy%20markets%20by%20potentially%20reducing%20oil%20demand%2C%20affecting%20oil%20prices%2C%20and%20altering%20trade%20dynamics.%20Achieving%20strategic%20autonomy%20in%20the%20EV%20sector%20is%20crucial%20for%20national%20security%20and%20requires%20investment%20in%20research%20and%20development%2C%20robust%20domestic%20supply%20chains%2C%20and%20innovation.%20A%20comprehensive%20strategy%20addressing%20supply%20chain%20vulnerabilities%20and%20fostering%20international%20partnerships%20is%20essential%20to%20enhance%20India's%20energy%20security%20and%20leadership%20in%20sustainable%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Lure%20Of%20Subsidies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumer%20interest%20in%20EVs%20is%20largely%20driven%20by%20heavy%20subsidies.%20The%20Central%20government%20has%20invested%20thousands%20of%20crores%20in%20these%20subsidies%20and%20state%20governments%20have%20lost%20significant%20revenue%20by%20offering%20low%20GST%20and%20road%20tax%20for%20EVs.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20lower%20untaxed%20cost%20of%20coal%20for%20charging%20makes%20EVs%20seem%20cheaper%20compared%20to%20heavily%20taxed%20petrol.%20However%2C%20the%20actual%20price%20of%20EVs%20remains%20high%20without%20these%20subsidies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20currently%20lacks%20the%20infrastructure%20for%20large-scale%20battery%20production%2C%20recycling%2C%20and%20disposal%2C%20posing%20significant%20environmental%20and%20logistical%20challenges.%20Though%20advances%20in%20battery%20recycling%20technologies%20are%20expected%20to%20reduce%20the%20environmental%20impact%20of%20battery%20production%20in%20the%20future%2C%20given%20the%20current%20complexities%20with%20EVs%2C%20we%20should%20probably%20take%20the%20middle%20road.%20A%20more%20pragmatic%20approach%20would%20be%20to%20promote%20hybrid%20vehicles%20in%20the%20transition%20period%2C%20which%20offer%20better%20fuel%20efficiency%20and%20lower%20emissions%20without%20the%20need%20for%20massive%20infrastructure%20overhauls.%20Reducing%20taxes%20on%20hybrids%20could%20make%20them%20more%20appealing%20to%20consumers%20without%20the%20need%20for%20substantial%20subsidies.%20Currently%2C%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20vehicles%20are%20subject%20to%20high%20taxation%2C%20and%20hybrid%20vehicles%20are%20taxed%20at%20the%20same%20rate.%20This%20doesn't%20make%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20also%20be%20patient%20until%20other%20countries%20address%20the%20problem%20on%20a%20large%20scale.%20Larger%20economies%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20experimenting%20and%20absorbing%20financial%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20India%20builds%20up%20its%20innovation%20capacity%20and%20relevant%20industrial%20capabilities%2C%20it%20would%20be%20foolhardy%20to%20rush%20with%20policy.%20It%20must%20balance%20the%20need%20to%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions%20with%20the%20practical%20challenges%20of%20energy%20production%2C%20infrastructure%20readiness%2C%20and%20economic%20viability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Arindam%20Goswami%C2%A0is%20a%20Research%20Scholar%20at%C2%A0Takshashila%C2%A0Institution%2C%20working%20in%20the%20High-Tech%20Geopolitics%20Programme)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719989100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F2udlhubo_ev_625x300_03_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-plan-to-go-all-ev-by-2034-can-backfire-disastrously-6023342%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20hidden%20carbon%20footprint%20of%20EVs%2C%20the%20inadequacy%20of%20our%20renewable%20energy%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20strain%20on%20our%20power%20grid%20and%20the%20economic%20and%20geopolitical%20ramifications%2C%20all%20paint%20a%20grim%20picture%20of%20a%20policy%20that%20could%20backfire%20disastrously.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-plan-to-go-all-ev-by-2034-can-backfire-disastrously-6023342%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproj