s%20Hathras%20has%20risen%20to%20121%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%5CnAccording%20to%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Relief%20Commissioner%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20injured%20in%20Tuesday's%20incident%20...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-toll-rises-to-121-fir-registered-against-organisers-124070300100_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-toll-rises-to-121-fir-registered-against-organisers-124070300100_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-toll-rises-to-121-fir-registered-against-organisers-124070300100_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi's%20%26quot%3BTumse%20Na%20Ho%20Payega%26quot%3B%20Swipe%20At%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Tuesday%20mounted%20a%20stinging%20counterattack%20on%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20he%20mocked%20him%20as%20'balak%20buddhi'%20(childish%20mind)%2C%20accused%20him%20of%20linking%20Hindus%20with%20violence%20and%20making%20false%20claims%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20and%20sought%20stringent%20action%20against%20him%20to%20protect%20parliamentary%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20nearly%2018-hour-long%20discussion%20on%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20on%20the%20President's%20Address%20in%20the%20Lower%20House%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20%26quot%3Becosystem%26quot%3B%20are%20working%20day%20and%20night%20to%20impress%20upon%20people%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20has%20been%20defeated%20in%20the%20elections%20despite%20voters%20handing%20his%20government%20a%20historic%20third-term%20for%20stability%20and%20continuity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20tell%20Congress%20leaders%20to%20not%20suppress%20people's%20mandate%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20fake%20victory%20celebrations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20and%20added%20the%20opposition%20party%20was%20behaving%20as%20if%20it%20had%20won%2099%20out%20100%20seats%20and%20not%20out%20of%20543%2C%20the%20actual%20strength%20of%20the%20House.%20The%20Congress%20turned%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bparasitic%20party%26quot%3B%20in%20these%20polls%2C%20feeding%20off%20its%20partners'%20votes%20to%20boost%20its%20tally%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20conceding%20defeat%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20behaving%20arrogantly%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20its%20cheerful%20response%20to%20the%20mandate%20is%20like%20a%20parent%20encouraging%20a%20child%20who%20has%20fallen%20off%20a%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20nearly%20135-minute%20speech%2C%20which%20saw%20continuous%20slogan-shouting%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20and%20heckling%20by%20opposition%20members%2C%20PM%20Modi%20turned%20his%20usual%20combative%20self%20after%20initially%20listing%20various%20successes%20of%20his%20government%20since%202014%20as%20he%20took%20on%20the%20Congress%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20without%20naming%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mandate%20for%20the%20Congress%20is%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20opposition%20and%20keep%20shouting%20once%20it%20runs%20out%20of%20logic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%20delivered%20its%20third%20worst%20performance%20in%20the%20national%20elections%20and%20failed%20to%20reach%20250-mark%20after%20the%201984%20polls%2C%20he%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BAaj%20desh%20inse%20kah%20raha%20hai%20-%20tumse%20na%20ho%20payega%20(Country%20is%20telling%20him%20that%20you%20are%20not%20up%20to%20it)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Congress%20became%20a%20%26quot%3Bparasitic%20party%26quot%3B%20in%20these%20polls%20as%20its%20tally%20of%2099%20was%20largely%20curtsey%20its%20allies%2C%20while%20it%20performed%20poorly%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20merely%2026%20per%20cent%20where%20the%20party%20was%20pitted%20directly%20against%20the%20BJP%20or%20was%20the%20main%20opposition%20force.%20Its%20strike%20rate%20rose%20to%2050%20per%20cent%20where%20it%20was%20a%20junior%20partner%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20won%20only%20two%20out%20of%2066%20seats%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20he%20said%20while%20contrasting%20the%20BJP's%20performance%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20well%20as%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Odisha%20where%20it%20formed%20its%20maiden%20government.%20The%20Congress%20is%20not%20visible%20even%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20microscope%20in%20four%20states%20where%20assembly%20polls%20were%20held%20while%20the%20NDA%20won%20an%20unprecedented%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20trying%20to%20spread%20anarchy%20through%20its%20economic%20policies%2C%20%26quot%3Bdivisive%26quot%3B%20politics%20around%20castes%20and%20regions%20and%20by%20raising%20doubts%20about%20India's%20democratic%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20the%20Congress%2C%20especially%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20his%20crosshairs%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20it%20has%20become%20addicted%20to%20lies%20like%20a%20man-eater%20animal%20to%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20witnessed%20childish%20conduct%20yesterday%2C%20he%20said%20of%20Gandhi's%20speech%20in%20which%20the%20Congress%20leader%20had%20targeted%20the%20government%20over%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%2C%20the%20MSP%20regime%20and%20the%20revamping%20work%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20violating%20tenets%20of%20Hinduism%20by%20allegedly%20spreading%20violence%20and%20hate%2C%20drawing%20massive%20protests%20by%20treasury%20benches.%20Many%20of%20his%20comments%20were%20later%20expunged%20by%20the%20Chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLaments%20of%20'balak%20buddhi'%20went%20on.%20'I%20have%20been%20beaten'.%20A%20new%20drama%20was%20rolled%20out%20to%20gain%20sympathy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20reference%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20charge%20that%20he%20was%20targeted%20in%20different%20criminal%20cases%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20is%20he%20is%20on%20bail%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20of%20thousands%20of%20crore%20of%20rupees%2C%20was%20convicted%20for%20calling%20an%20OBC%20community%20thief%20and%20had%20to%20tender%20an%20apology%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20speaking%20lies%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20been%20facing%20several%20cases%20of%20defamation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%26quot%3Bbalak%20buddhi%26quot%3B%20at%20times%20tries%20to%20hug%20someone%20in%20the%20House%20and%20sometime%20winks%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20tainting%20Parliament's%20decorum%20with%20his%20conduct%20despite%20being%20a%20many-term%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BParliament%20was%20misled%20yesterday.%20Parliamentary%20democracy%20cannot%20be%20protected%20without%20taking%20the%20issue%20seriously.%26quot%3B%20He%20told%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20that%20the%20House%20and%20the%20country%20expect%20him%20to%20take%20stringent%20action%20to%20stop%20this%20practice%20of%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20present%20in%20the%20House%2C%20was%20reprimanded%20by%20Birla%20for%20nudging%20opposition%20members%20to%20enter%20the%20Well%20to%20protest%20during%20PM%20Modi's%20speech%2C%20and%20the%20House%20later%20passed%20a%20motion%20moved%20by%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20seconded%20by%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20to%20condemn%20the%20opposition's%20obstructionist%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20seasoned%20leaders%20of%20the%20party%20choose%20this%20path%20of%20anarchy%2C%20it%20shows%20that%20the%20country%20is%20headed%20for%20trouble%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said.%20He%20asked%20opposition%20parties%20to%20work%20with%20the%20government%20on%20issues%20of%20national%20interest%20but%20kept%20the%20heat%20on%20Gandhi%20as%20he%20concluded%20his%20speech%20by%20wishing%20that%20the%20God%20grant%20good%20sense%20to%20%26quot%3Bbalak%20buddhi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlamming%20Gandhi%20over%20his%20reference%20to%20Hinduism%2C%20he%20said%20Hinuds%20were%20linked%20to%20violence%20even%20though%20it%20is%20their%20tolerance%20which%20has%20allowed%20diversity%20to%20bloom%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20this%20your%20values%20and%20mindset%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%2C%20claiming%20that%20a%20conspiracy%20is%20being%20hatched%20to%20target%20the%20community%20and%20people%20will%20not%20forgive%20such%20conduct%20for%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20spreading%20brazen%20lies%20on%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20to%20discourage%20youngsters%20from%20joining%20forces%20and%20weaken%20his%20government's%20efforts%20to%20strengthen%20India's%20military%20might.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20scams%20and%20neglect%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20for%20decades%20weakened%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20while%20he%20has%20been%20working%20to%20reform%20and%20modernise%20the%20defence%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurning%20to%20paper%20leaks%2C%20he%20said%20his%20government%20is%20taking%20steps%20on%20a%20war-footing%20to%20prevent%20their%20recurrence%20and%20that%20the%20guilty%20will%20not%20be%20spared.%20Arrests%20are%20taking%20place%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20have%20seen%20that%20we%20have%20worked%20with%20dedication%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20fulfilling%20the%20mantra%20of%20'public%20service%20is%20God's%20service'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20said%20he%20can%20understand%20the%20pain%20of%20some%20who%20despite%20spreading%20lies%20and%20mislea