this%20spark%20of%20hope%20kept%20her%20dreams%20alive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20the%20case%20of%20any%20race%2C%20cheerleaders%20are%20essential.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20I%20had%20invaluable%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sakshi%20referring%20to%20her%20mother%2C%20father%2C%20sister%20and%20grandparents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20ensured%20they%20were%20positive%20when%20around%20her%2C%20it%20was%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Sneha%20points%20out%2C%20watching%20one%E2%80%99s%20child%20in%20pain%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20things%20to%20go%20through%20as%20a%20parent.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%20came%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354377%2Fkerala-r-vishwan-honey-farmer-abandoned-child-bee-rearing-beekeeping-training-profits-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20challenge%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20broke%20down%20many%20times%20seeing%20the%20pain%20she%20was%20in.%20It%20was%20heartbreaking%20to%20watch%20an%20all-rounder%20and%20multi-talented%20girl%20not%20even%20being%20able%20to%20sit%2C%20stand%20or%20hold%20anything.%20The%20initial%20days%20were%20so%20tough%20that%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20think%20or%20comprehend%20anything.%20I%20would%20simply%20follow%20the%20instructions%20given%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sakshi%20underwent%20more%20than%2020%20surgeries%20to%20fix%20her%20injuries%20and%20she%20says%20recovery%20is%20still%20on%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354581%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESakshi%20underwent%20more%20than%2020%20surgeries%20to%20fix%20her%20injuries%20and%20she%20says%20recovery%20is%20still%20on%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sakshi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20this%20challenging%20scene%20that%20Sakshi%20announced%20her%20decision%20to%20continue%20her%20MBBS%20studies.%20Everyone%20was%20taken%20aback%2C%20particularly%20her%20friends%2C%20colleagues%20and%20professors%2C%20she%20says%2C%20who%20thought%20she%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20resume%20studies%20so%20quickly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20hindsight%2C%20she%20feels%20it%20was%20the%20right%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20accelerated%20my%20recovery%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20being%20unable%20to%20hold%20a%20pen%20to%20securing%20a%20distinction%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20Sakshi%20on%20her%20feet%20took%20a%20village.%20Everyone%20played%20their%20part%20well%2C%20she%20notes%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20dad%20formed%20a%20core%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311674%2Fkolkata-samriddhi-malhotra-transforming-life-after-abusive-marriage-yoga-breathwork-goa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20support%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20would%20set%20mini%20goals%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESakshi%20goes%20on%20to%20share%20an%20anecdote%20of%20the%20time%20she%20had%20just%20started%20to%20use%20the%20walker.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20very%20painful.%20I%20could%20hardly%20go%20out%20of%20the%20room%20before%20wanting%20to%20give%20up%20and%20get%20back%20to%20bed.%20But%20my%20dad%20made%20a%20rule%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20felt%20like%20giving%20up%2C%20I%20would%20take%20five%20more%20steps%20and%20then%20make%20a%20U-turn%20back%20to%20the%20room.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20small%20motivations%20made%20Sakshi%E2%80%99s%20recovery%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatching%20Sakshi%E2%80%99s%20journey%20unravel%20has%20been%20all-inspiring%20to%20many%2C%20particularly%20her%20sister%20Isha%2C%20who%20looks%20up%20to%20her%20as%20a%20role%20model.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20many%20younger%20siblings%20get%20the%20opportunity%20to%20see%20their%20elder%20siblings%20grow%20up%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20I%20salute%20her%20willpower%20and%20I%20often%20tell%20her%20that%20she%20is%20the%20main%20character%20of%20my%20life!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsha%20smiles%20as%20she%20remembers%20the%20day%20her%20%3Cem%3Edidi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(elder%20sister)%20got%20admission%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F170564%2Fahmedabad-uttarayan-rescue-crane-doc-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorthopaedics%20%3C%2Fa%3Edepartment%20at%20the%20BJ%20Medical%20College%2C%20Ahmedabad.%20%E2%80%9CI%20baked%20a%20cake%20and%20we%20celebrated%20it%20like%20a%20festival!%E2%80%9D%20she%20exclaims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdversity%20had%20taught%20the%20family%20to%20cherish%20the%20small%20wins.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20the%20first%20time%20after%20the%20accident%20when%20my%20sister%20was%20able%20to%20open%20the%20cap%20on%20the%20toothpaste%20tube%20and%20brush%20her%20teeth%20by%20herself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Isha%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20th