With%20her%20coconut%20based%20products%2C%20she%20has%20developed%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20Malaysia.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20inquiries%20came%2C%20I%20started%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20product%20and%20understand%20its%20importance.%20This%20is%20when%20I%20got%20passionate%20about%20the%20coconut%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20job%20experience%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20her%20entrepreneurial%20journey%20and%20in%202021%2C%20she%20formally%20launched%20her%20company%20%E2%80%98Greenaura%E2%80%99%20that%20sells%2013%20coconut-based%20products%20including%20virgin%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F314028%2Ffarmers-son-uses-zero-waste-farming-to-make-coconut-products-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20coconut%20oil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20milk%20powder%2C%20vinegar%2C%20curry%20powder%2C%20chutney%2C%20and%20pickle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20Sumila%20says%2C%20she%20makes%20an%20average%20sale%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20in%20a%20month.%20Interestingly%2C%20delivering%20through%20her%20website%2C%20she%20has%20developed%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20Malaysia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20homemaker%20to%20an%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pharmacognosyasia.com%2FFiles%2FOther%2FAJPV5I4p0519.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2021%20study%20%3C%2Fa%3Epublished%20in%20the%20Asian%20Journal%20of%20Pharmacognosy%20termed%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98miracle%20oil%E2%80%99.%20The%20study%20mentions%20that%20the%20oil%20has%20antioxidant%2C%20anti-inflammatory%2C%20and%20immunomodulatory%2C%20anti-hyperli