3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Beyond%20Pride%20Month%E2%80%99%3A%20An%2018-YO%20is%20On%20a%20Mission%20to%20Help%20Trans%20Persons%20Revive%20Their%20Businesses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20residents%20living%20near%20VIP%20Road%2C%20Zirakpur%2C%20Punjab%2C%20a%20usual%20way%20to%20celebrate%20the%20end%20of%20the%20work%20day%20is%20a%20fiesta%20at%20a%20food%20truck%20run%20by%20Dhananjay%20Chauhan%20(she%2Fher).%20But%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20first%20case%20of%20Dhananjay%20cooking%20up%20a%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20recall%20how%20in%202016%2C%20Panjab%20University%20made%20headlines%20for%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20first%20public%20universities%20in%20India%20to%20build%20a%20separate%20washroom%20for%20trans%20students%20on%20campus.%20If%20you%E2%80%99re%20looking%20for%20the%20source%20of%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338067%2Fbengaluru-transwoman-helps-abandoned-eldery-orphans-food-shelter-ngo-nammane-summane-impact-appeal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevolutionary%20step%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20look%20no%20further%20than%20Dhananjay%2C%20who%20still%20carries%20her%20moniker%20of%20being%20%E2%80%98Chandigarh%E2%80%99s%20first%20transgender%20student%E2%80%99%20with%20great%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20conversation%20with%20her%20reveals%2C%20right%20from%20the%20onset%2C%20Dhananjay%20has%20attempted%20to%20break%20glass%20ceilings%20whenever%20she%20comes%20across%20one.%20And%20the%20food%20truck%20that%20she%20runs%20from%205%20pm%20to%2011%20pm%20every%20evening%20is%20no%20exception.%20In%20the%20minutes%20she%20has%20to%20spare%20between%20doling%20out%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20spring%20rolls%2C%20pasta%2C%20fried%20rice%2C%20noodles%20and%20other%20delicious%20fast%20food%20to%20the%20many%20patrons%20who%20flock%20to%20the%20truck%2C%20Dhananjay%20lets%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%20on%20how%20a%20trans%20identity%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20translate%20to%20giving%20up%20on%20one%E2%80%99s%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20food%20truck%20could%20speak%2C%20it%20would%20have%20a%20compelling%20tale%20to%20tell.%20In%20June%202021%2C%20actor%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%20who%20was%20promoting%20his%20film%20%E2%80%98Chandigarh%20Kare%20Aashiqui%E2%80%99%20first%20donated%20the%20truck%20to%20Dhananjay.%20However%2C%20what%20was%20meant%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20her%20be%20financially%20independent%20had%20the%20opposite%20effect%20when%20local%20authorities%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20her%20to%20run%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20denied%20a%20license%20and%20the%20truck%20had%20to%20be%20parked%20in%20a%20nearby%20school%20for%20almost%20a%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dhananjay%20says.%20But%20today%2C%20things%20have%20changed%20for%20the%20better.%20While%20she%20shares%20that%20sales%20are%20not%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%20currently%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CThe%20heat%20is%20too%20much%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20many%20customers%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20she%20maintains%20that%20at%20least%20she%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F256969%2Fmumbai-heroes-of-humanity-humanity-heroes-first-transgender-photojournalist-zoya-thomas-lobo-transgender-community-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20business%20to%20call%20her%20own%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20story%20is%20a%20testament%20of%20reform%20and%20promise%3B%20it%20is%20also%20a%20nod%20to%2018-year-old%20Ishnoor%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20help%20the%20trans%20community%20regain%20their%20footing%20in%20the%20quest%20for%20financial%20independence.%20His%20endeavour%20to%20help%20trans%20persons%20revive%20their%20businesses%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20%E2%80%98SoulSpectrum%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20small%20but%20significant%20step%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20bringing%20a%20radical%20shift%20in%20the%20way%20businesses%20run%20by%20trans%20individuals%20are%20perceived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0015-1-1719562699-500x474.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dhananjay%20Chauhan%20in%20front%20of%20her%20food%20truck%20'Sweekar'%20that%20she%20runs%20with%20Rudrapratap%20Singh%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0015-1-1719562699-500x474.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0015-1-1719562699-300x284.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0015-1-1719562699-768x727.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0015-1-1719562699-150x142.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0015-1-1719562699.jpg%201170w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354772%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22474%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDhananjay%20Chauhan%20in%20front%20of%20her%20food%20truck%20%E2%80%98Sweekar%E2%80%99%20that%20she%20runs%20with%20Rudrapratap%20Singh%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ishnoor%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98It%20goes%20beyond%20Pride%20Month%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20do%20trans%20people%20have%20to%20be%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20trolls%3F%E2%80%9D%20Ishnoor%20wondered%20as%20he%20scrolled%20through%20social%20media%20during%20his%20school%20break%20last%20year.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20negative%20comments%20on%20videos%20that%20featured%20trans%20people%20were%20never-ending%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Class%2012%20student%20of%20Vivek%20High%20School%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20was%20baffled%20by%20this%20blind-sided%20hate.%20He%20was%20even%20more%20amused%20when%20the%20rhetoric%20would%20witness%20a%20flip%20during%20Pride%20Month.%20And%20this%20made%20him%20think%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20starting%20an%20initiative%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334508%2Finspiring-story-of-sex-worker-turned-artist-aravani-art-project-for-transgenders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20trans%20persons%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20that%20would%20make%20their%20%5Btrans%20persons%E2%80%99%5D%20struggles%20an%20ongoing%20subject%20of%20conversation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ishnoor%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20put%20a%20finger%20on%20a%20formal%20model%2C%20it%20was%20a%20chance%20meeting%20with%20Dhananjay%20that%20gave%20his%20vision%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20conversation%20ensued%2C%20the%20latter%20began%20to%20relay%20the%20struggle%20she%20had%20to%20endure%20to%20get%20her%20food%20truck%20up%20and%20running.%20%E2%80%9CDhananjay%20recounted%20how%20the%20local%20administrations%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20supportive%20and%20getting%20permissions%20was%20a%20hassle.%20She%20was%20disappointed%20at%20how%20the%20truck%20was%20simply%20wasting%20away%20and%20not%20helping%20her%20generate%20income%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20the%20intention%20with%20which%20it%20was%20donated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ishnoor%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fz3LszbYKybU%3Fsi%3D0R-uN-RJRZY1_hft%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGathering%20a%20couple%20of%20his%20friends%2C%20Ishnoor%20began%20