s%20that%20destroyed%20crops%20at%20night%20%E2%80%94%20all%20this%20during%20the%201970s.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20have%20never%20stolen%20anything%20but%20I%20had%20to.%20I%20have%20only%20stolen%20food%20items%2C%20that%20too%20due%20to%20unbearable%20hunger%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20time%2C%20he%20got%20caught%20while%20stealing%2C%20but%20the%20owner%20was%20a%20kind%20man.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20explained%20that%20I%20stole%20because%20of%20hunger%20and%20I%20had%20no%20one%20to%20care%20for%20me%2C%20the%20man%20asked%20him%20to%20graze%20his%20cattle%20and%20gave%20him%2015%20paise%20per%20day%20as%20a%20wage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20grazing%20cattle%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332769%2Fgeorge-remedios-plants-food-forests-trees-in-mumbai-limited-spaces-rooftop-gardens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20forest%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Nilambur%2C%20he%20noticed%20honeycombs%20and%20honey%20bees%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Soon%2C%20those%20honeycombs%20became%20a%20source%20of%20filling%20his%20stomach.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20hungry%2C%20I%20collected%20honey%20and%20drank%20it.%20Of%20course%2C%20I%20would%20get%20bitten%20sometimes%2C%20but%20hunger%20is%20your%20greatest%20shield%20at%20such%20times.%20One%20of%20those%20days%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20I%20keep%20them%2C%20then%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20wander%20around%20to%20find%20the%20honeycombs%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20to%20a%20nearby%20shop%20and%20got%20a%20wooden%20box%20that%20was%20used%20to%20keep%20tomatoes%20for%20free.%20%E2%80%9CI%20kept%20the%20honey%20bees%20inside%20it.%20That%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20it%20all.%20Without%20knowing%20any%20scientific%20methods%20of%20keeping%20honey%20bees%20or%20collecting%20honey%2C%20I%20just%20dived%20into%20it%20due%20to%20sheer%20necessity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20initially%20burnt%20the%20honeycomb%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F219387%2Fpunjab-organic-farming-honey-earns-lakhs-women-empowerment-rural-inspiring-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20collect%20honey%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20got%20a%20tin%20full%20of%20honey%20and%20went%20to%20Kozhikode%20to%20sell%20it.%20I%20was%20only%2013%20years%20old%20at%20the%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20sold%20the%20honey%20to%20the%20Kozhikode%20Sarvodaya%20Sangham%20under%20the%20Kerala%20Khadi%20Board%20for%20only%20Rs%20328.%20%E2%80%9CI%20still%20sell%20a%20portion%20of%20my%20produce%20to%20the%20institution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20honey%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20accidentally%20stepped%20into%20the%20world%20of%20honey%20farming%2C%20Vishwan%20learnt%20along%20the%20way.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20an%20expert%20and%20did%20not%20know%20anything%20about%20farming.%20My%20initial%20investment%20was%20only%20Rs%20328%20%E2%80%94%20the%20money%20I%20got%20from%20selling%20my%20first-ever%20batch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelieving%20that%20it%20was%20destiny%20and%20the%20work%20of%20god%20to%20introduce%20him%20to%20honey%20farming%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20worldly%20experience%20or%20formal%20education.%20There%20was%20no%20one%20to%20help%20me.%20Had%20I%20not%20found%20out%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F113516%2Fconcerned-citizens-forum-thane-takes-up-beekeeping%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20occupation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20what%20I%20would%20have%20done.%20Honey%20was%20the%20only%20kind%20of%20farming%20that%20required%20the%