ion%20and%20effective%20discipline.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWorking%20with%20parents%20across%20diverse%20groups%20in%20multiple%20languages%20in%20schools%20(both%20private%20and%20government)%2C%20corporates%2C%20and%20at%20an%20individual%20level%2C%20Parenting%20Matters%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20conviction%20that%20by%20supporting%20families%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20transformation%20towards%20a%20healthier%20and%20more%20caring%20community%2C%20one%20family%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719408628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parenting%20Matters%20has%20been%20working%20with%20parents%20for%20over%2020%20years%20to%20help%20them%20figure%20out%20effective%20and%20sensitive%20ways%20to%20raise%20their%20children.%20Their%20main%20focus%20is%20to%20undo%20the%20past%20where%20anger%2C%20intolerance%2C%20and%20disrespect%20governed%20parent-children%20relationships.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354393%2Fhow-to-improve-your-parenting-skills-ten-lessons-tips-tricks-from-parents-parenting-matters-workshops%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Assam%2C%20Solar%20Energy%20Helps%20Doctors%20%26amp%3B%20Medicines%20Reach%20Island%20Dwellers%20on%20Boats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20June%2C%20check%20out%20our%20%23ApnaGharSolar%20series%2C%20an%20exclusive%20deep%20dive%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.solarsquare.in%2F%3Futm_source%3Dsocialmedia%26utm_medium%3Dad%26utm_campaign%3DTheBetterIndia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESolarSquare%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20solar%20power%20boom.%20Stay%20tu